    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >See the world through the eyes of <strong>SomeCompany</strong>'s agents. Gain and use parkour abilities to become <i>the fastest</i> in the world. Follow company's plan and don't forget to take your pills... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357740/extras/94ab5e71f716ff011b7fdc6938876292.avif?t=1765142587\" width=617 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Double jump, wallrunning, stomp and dash - utilize them all to complete the levels quickly. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357740/extras/05ae1ea0fadb895b0287a0635b2c6619.poster.avif?t=1765142587\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357740/extras/05ae1ea0fadb895b0287a0635b2c6619.webm?t=1765142587\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357740/extras/05ae1ea0fadb895b0287a0635b2c6619.mp4?t=1765142587\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357740/extras/affb59e4a3a2eb34fbc8edf7fcaeca9d.avif?t=1765142587\" width=617 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight with your foes using bow and sword, gain time by defeating them and don't let them kill you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357740/extras/911d418acc4765b4b997aaedb71711c7.poster.avif?t=1765142587\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357740/extras/911d418acc4765b4b997aaedb71711c7.webm?t=1765142587\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357740/extras/911d418acc4765b4b997aaedb71711c7.mp4?t=1765142587\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357740/extras/d75264c86ff5b49cd86ecf233756235d.avif?t=1765142587\" width=617 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run as fast as you can through six chapters of levels with different low-poly environments and distinctive music. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357740/extras/6b6d2ceed4edfbf03c317bed55f3ba26.poster.avif?t=1765142587\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357740/extras/6b6d2ceed4edfbf03c317bed55f3ba26.webm?t=1765142587\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357740/extras/6b6d2ceed4edfbf03c317bed55f3ba26.mp4?t=1765142587\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357740/extras/9f5f072659a393d80640fd50d2a72a8a.avif?t=1765142587\" width=617 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reach bronze, silver, gold and ultimately diamond medal. Prove you're a valuable asset for the company. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357740/extras/91625b4c67ee1aaff3e92a77e21fb0fb.poster.avif?t=1765142587\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357740/extras/91625b4c67ee1aaff3e92a77e21fb0fb.webm?t=1765142587\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357740/extras/91625b4c67ee1aaff3e92a77e21fb0fb.mp4?t=1765142587\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357740/extras/60fb6eb901cc54ae742ac37efd093cd7.avif?t=1765142587\" width=617 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete with other players and become the most renowned agent in the world. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357740/extras/d09a00b650b004f056af0703cbb69a0a.poster.avif?t=1765142587\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357740/extras/d09a00b650b004f056af0703cbb69a0a.webm?t=1765142587\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357740/extras/d09a00b650b004f056af0703cbb69a0a.mp4?t=1765142587\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
